<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5219526>
    dc:description "Figure 3. (A–E) Colastes (Fungivenator) fritzeni, holotype, female; (F) Colastes (Colastes) braconius Haliday, Belgium, near Antwerp, female. (A) Part of forewing; (B, F) head, lateral aspect; (C) apex of antenna; (D) hind leg; (E) first metasomal tergite, dorsal aspect. Scales: 1.0×scale bar (A); 1.5×(B); 1.9×(C); 1.1×(D); 1.3×(E); 2.0×(F)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5219526/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

